  m_Maskable: 1
  m_OnCullStateChanged:
    m_PersistentCalls:
      m_Calls: []
  m_text: '                                            INSTRUCTIONS


    1) WASD
    to Move and SPACE to Jump

    2) Left Shift to Dash

    3) Rotate the Camera
    using Mouse

    4) Press Left Mouse Button to Shoot

    5) Rockets can only
    hit within a specific range, When an Enemy is in Range, a Marker appears on then
    for Auto-Aiming

    6) We can manually aim by long holding Left Mouse Button
    and draging the Mouse on the desired enemy and then releasing it

    7) You
    have to stand on the Blue Color Circle on the Map to score points, These are
    called Domination Zones

    8) Open Pause Screen using Esc'
